index 0000000..b4258ce
--- /dev/null
+++ b/.slime/PRUNED.md
@@ -0,0 +1,8 @@
+# Pruned
+
+- A stats registry / strategy / base-class per metric. Rejected: only one stat
+  (total) is required now; ≥2 real variants needed before abstracting. A single
+  `store.stats()` returning a dict is enough room for future metrics.
+- Computing the count in cli.py via `len(store.load(...))`. Rejected in favor of
+  a `store.stats()` seam so future stats (avg length, oldest/newest) compute in
+  one place over the notes list, not scattered in the CLI.
diff --git a/.slime/corridor.md b/.slime/corridor.md
new file mode 100644
