--- /dev/null
+++ b/.slime/corridor.md
@@ -0,0 +1,10 @@
+# Corridor: E2-B-2-stats
+
+Goal: a `stats` command that prints the integer total number of notes.
+Seam: cli.build_parser() registers `cmd_*` subcommands; store.load() yields the notes list.
+Future stats (avg length, oldest/newest) slot into a single store.stats() dict — no new abstraction now.
+
+## Paths
+- cli_notes/cli.py
+- cli_notes/store.py
+- tests/test_cli.py
